          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-3">5. Service Changes</h2>
          <p>We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or terminate the service at any time without notice. We may also update these terms from time to time, and we recommend that you review the latest version regularly.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-3">6. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have any questions about these terms or need further information, please contact us at:</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><a href="mailto:icnych@gmail.com" class="text-yellow-400 hover:underline">icnych@gmail.com</a></p>
        </section>
